column5: Anyone looking for a partner on Simcoe this week? Haven't been out in a while. Willing to share expenses.  Thanks guys,  Curt
Unless you're a duck, it doesn't look too good for the weather,  right miserable.
lol.  I hadn't checked the weather report for this week.
Looks like 7 days and 7 nights ,sure not making it easy around here.I'm sure things will change before the weekend.I hope !!!!!!!!!!!!!

~~~Was out on past Sunday off Pephpherlaw, great weather plus 10 wind out of the west at 15, small armada of boats just off the mouth, many a dink were tossed back. may be headed out this weekend again, Sat. & Sun.
Going to the trailer park for the weekend. Was hoping to get out with someone during the week. Maybe next week will be better
